@NODE "11what" "Was ist little Icons"
@NEXT "12why"
@PREV "main"
@TOC "MAIN"
 1.1. What is it?
 
 @{fg shine}little Icons@{fg text} is a set of icons

 for Magic-Workbench (8 color icons).

 In the subdir little are little Icons (you also can use them as Dockbrushes).

 In the subdir big are some other bigger icons.

 Some Drawer Icons are in the subdir drawers.

 Icons for Drives are in the subdir drives (you cannot see them from WB).

 If you want to see some screen-shots look in subdir pics.





@ENDNODE

@NODE "12why" "Warum gibt es little Icons"
@NEXT "13require"
@PREV "11what"
@TOC "MAIN"
 1.2. Why did I produce it?

I only work in Hires-Screenmode (724x283) so there is not much place on my WB.

So I decide to make little Icons because I wanted to have Dockicons for Toolmanager on my WB.

The biggest problem were the big drawers (mostly were the same)
icons so I made little ones (they save much place on WB and some on HD).

See the Screenshots !!!

@ENDNODE

@NODE "13require" "Was braucht man f³r little Icons?"
@NEXT "14install"
@PREV "12why"
@TOC "MAIN"
1.3. Requirements

First you need an AMIGA.

Then you need a 8 color WB.

A Screenshot of your WB (@{"to send" LINK "24distrib"} @{"me" LINK "21author"}).

Thats all !!!


@ENDNODE

@NODE "14install" "Wie wird little Icons installiert?"
@NEXT "15use"
@PREV "13require"
@TOC "MAIN"
 1.4. Installation

Replace you old icons with my ones
(its easier if you use a tool like MuiReIcon)

@ENDNODE

